1. setting up prisma in backend npm i prisma in backend 
2. npm i @prism/client 
3. npx prisma init for prisma folder 
4. check docker is installed or not 
5. cmd for postgres in docker $ docker run --name my-postgres \
  -e POSTGRES_USER=myuser \
  -e POSTGRES_PASSWORD=mypassword \
  -p 5432:5432 \
  -d postgres

6. adding models in schema prisma 
7. npx prisma generate to generate file 
8. here ismy new env DATABASE_URL="postgresql://myuser:mypassword@localhost:5432/leetlab?schema=public"
9.  npx prisma migrate dev 
10. npx prisma db push to upload push data 

chapter-1 completed prisma setup 